caption: I think most of us had big plans for how we would have fun and a list of things we’d do once we started working and earning our own money. But somewhere along the way, the stress of keeping up with work, responsibilities, and living alone made us lose ourselves in the process.I know that balancing everything in life is challenging, but I believe that no matter how busy we get, we NEED to find time for ourselves and make space for things that make us feel happy to be alive. Otherwise, what’s the point?After spending hours and hours on screen, a trekking vacation is the perfect way to get away from everything, spend time in nature, and challenge yourself physically. Aayush is an amazing guy and he was the perfect company for this trip; seeing him smile, giggle, and be happy throughout made me realise that we need to keep making plans that make us EXCITED about life.There will always be the next big target to chase, the next work deadline that needs to be met, or the next promotion that we have to pursue. But let’s not forget that we only have one life, and we’re young only once. Once that time is gone, it’s never coming back. So let’s just make the most of it.•ad | @bookmyshowin Content writing by: @roshan__kumar
